::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer slows down as he sees a bot in the distance. It looked to be a 
femm, and was holding something in her hands. Stun gun ready, DevilDuer 
slowly starts to walk toward her.

"Don't fire unless she ain't friendly," he says to Hurricane, slowly 
aproaching Lady Hawk.
